<!--template match = paragraph--><p>
Remarks.
We could not locate 
syntype
specimens labelled “Moupin”. The only female 
syntype
found was the one mentioned here from Chang Yang. As this specimen bears the original handwriting of Fairmaire, as well as a “type” label, we suspect that the type locality was errorneously lisited in the original publication.
</p>
